## Description {#details}

<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/object/machobindentry">MachOBindEntry</a> encapsulates the current state in the decompression of binding opcodes.

This allows you to iterate through the compressed table of bindings using: <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/error">Error</a> Err = <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/error/#a4dfd0813c3d0e0a30439b5a3e9196b59">Error::success()</a>; for (const <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/object/machobindentry">llvm::object::MachOBindEntry</a> &amp;Entry : Obj-&gt;bindTable(&amp;Err)) &#123; &#125; if (Err) &#123; report error ...
